::Shadow Wing::

She woke up with a jerk.  She wondered what made her wake up so fast. She 
looked around i the cavern. She was high up on the cavern wall, perched on 
her ledge.  The air was warm and moist from the spring.  She thought that 
maybe she was just hot and needed to cool down.  She spread her wings and 
was about to take to flight.  Then she caught a moving shadow. She sensed 
Predacon.  How did he find me, she thought.  She knew that he blocked the 
main entrance to the cave.  She looked and saw  only a 30 foot clearance 
above the bot standing in the shadows.  it would be tight, but she could fly 
very fast.  She took a deep breath and flew off the ledge.  She flew over 
the head of the bot without making a sound.  Her head was only an inch from 
the cave ceiling.  She hoped that with her dark feathers, the bot would not 
notice her flying overhead and trying to leave the cave.
